      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BEAUTIFUL MAGPIE (1) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.79. Draws the cherry and has the ability and in winning form. Form reads well for this. MISS PENELOPE (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (30.65) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Expected to give a good account. CURRENCY KEEPING (7) turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (30.31) last time in a Mix at Richmond. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Has ability and can atone. WINIFRED NORA (5) looks a top-three chance while fresh.",
